  "texts": [
    "We firstly inferred the results by using the available pretrained LLMs.",
    "GPT-2 model source has been made publicly available, we used TFGPT2LMHeadModel as the pretrained GPT-2 model to test its ability in this NER task [57].",
    "Llama 2 is also an open-source LLM, which can be accessed through MetaAI [56].",
    "To evaluate the performance of the pre-trained models, we conducted several experiments, selecting the temperature and max tokens settings (shown in Table 1) that yielded the best results.",
    "Temperature, a hyperparameter, influences the randomness of the generated text."
